Class CompareNullSafe<T>

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:

BrowserOperatingSystemMappingComparator, IdentifiableComparator, OrderedPatternComparator
public abstract class CompareNullSafe<T>
extends Object
implements Comparator<T>, Serializable

Compares two references to each other and null is assumed to be less than a non-null value. This class provides the first check for null safe comparison.

Author:
André Rouél
